@startuml
' ─── Runtime Sequence for Feature Module ───
scale 0.8

actor "User" as User

participant "DI Module"           as DI
participant "UI Components"       as UI
participant "Screen ViewModel"    as SVM
participant "UseCase"             as UC
participant "Repository"          as REP
participant "Local DataSource"    as LDS
participant "Remote DataSource"   as RDS
participant "Graph ViewModel"     as GVM
participant "Navigation"          as NAV

== App Start / Dependency Injection ==
User -> DI: initializeApp()
activate DI
DI --> SVM: inject(screen viewmodel)
DI --> GVM: inject(graph viewmodel)
DI --> UC : inject(usecases)
DI --> REP: inject(repository)
DI --> LDS: inject(local data source)
DI --> RDS: inject(remote data source)
deactivate DI

== Screen Rendering Flow ==
User -> UI: displayScreen()
activate UI
UI -> SVM: onCreate()
activate SVM
SVM -> UC: loadInitialData()
activate UC
UC -> REP: getData()
activate REP
REP -> LDS: queryCache()
activate LDS
LDS --> REP: returnCachedData
deactivate LDS
REP -> RDS: fetchRemoteData()
activate RDS
RDS --> REP: returnRemoteData
deactivate RDS
REP --> UC: apiData
deactivate REP
UC --> SVM: domainData (map to domain model)
deactivate UC
SVM --> UI: render(uiData)  (map to UI model)
deactivate SVM

== Navigation & State Sharing ==
User -> NAV: navigate("NextScreen")
activate NAV
NAV -> GVM: storeState(domainData)  (use domain data for state)
activate GVM
GVM --> NAV: ack
deactivate GVM
NAV -> UI: showNextScreen()
deactivate NAV
UI -> SVM: onResume()
activate SVM
SVM -> GVM: retrieveState()
activate GVM
GVM --> SVM: stateData
deactivate GVM
SVM --> UI: render(stateData)
deactivate SVM

@enduml